---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import FAQ from "../components/FAQ.astro";
import { Moon, Droplet, Shield, Crosshair, ArrowRight, Skull } from "lucide-react";

// Keyword target: "bizarre lineage night vampire" (3-5% density conceptually)
const faqs = [
  {
    question: "How do I become a bizarre lineage night vampire?",
    answer: "To unlock the bizarre lineage night vampire subclass, you must locate the ancient stone mask during the night cycle and offer enough blood items. Once you equip the mask, you permanently transform into a bizarre lineage night vampire."
  },
  {
    question: "Does the bizarre lineage night vampire burn in the sun?",
    answer: "Yes, the defining weakness of a bizarre lineage night vampire is sunlight. If a bizarre lineage night vampire stays in direct sunlight without a protective umbrella item, their health rapidly depletes."
  },
  {
    question: "What is the best Stand for a bizarre lineage night vampire?",
    answer: "The bizarre lineage night vampire pairs exceptionally well with close-range power type Stands like The World or King Crimson. The added health regeneration makes the bizarre lineage night vampire incredibly tanky in PvP."
  },
  {
    question: "Can a bizarre lineage night vampire use Hamon?",
    answer: "No, a bizarre lineage night vampire cannot learn or use Hamon abilities. Attempting to use Hamon as a bizarre lineage night vampire will instantly result in your character's death."
  },
  {
    question: "How does a bizarre lineage night vampire heal?",
    answer: "A bizarre lineage night vampire heals by using the Blood Suck ability on NPCs or other players. This mechanic gives the bizarre lineage night vampire unmatched sustainability in long chaotic battles."
  }
];
---

<Layout
  title="Bizarre Lineage Night Vampire — Complete Race Guide & Best Builds"
  description="Master the bizarre lineage night vampire playstyle. Learn how to transform, avoid sunlight, optimize your build, and dominate PvP as a bizarre lineage night vampire."
  canonicalPath="/bizarre-lineage-night-vampire"
>
  <!-- HERO SECTION -->
  <section class="hero-section">
    <div class="container hero-content animate-fade-in">
      <div class="hero-badge">
        <span class="pulse-dot"></span>
        Sub-Ability Guide
      </div>
      
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        <span class="gradient-text">Bizarre Lineage Night Vampire</span> Guide
      </h1>
      
      <p class="hero-desc">
        Embrace the darkness and become a terrifying bizarre lineage night vampire. Unlock unmatched regeneration, superhuman strength, and devastating drain attacks. As a bizarre lineage night vampire, you sacrifice daylight for ultimate power in the shadows.
      </p>
      
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="#vampire-guide" class="btn btn-primary btn-glow">Become a Bizarre Lineage Night Vampire</a>
        <a href="/tier-list" class="btn btn-secondary glass-btn">View Best Vampire Stands</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ADVANTAGES / WHY USE IT -->
  <section class="intro-section section">
    <div class="container intro-content">
      <h2 class="section-title">Why Play as a Bizarre Lineage Night Vampire?</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        Sustain, damage, and pure intimidation. The bizarre lineage night vampire is arguably the best subclass for aggressive players.
      </p>
      <p class="intro-body">
        Choosing to become a bizarre lineage night vampire drastically shifts how you approach the game. You trade the freedom of daytime exploration for the immense combat advantages of the night. A well-built bizarre lineage night vampire can out-heal incoming damage during intense 1v1 duels, making them nearly unkillable. With increased movement speed and modified dash mechanics, a bizarre lineage night vampire controls the pacing of any fight.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FEATURES BENTO GRID -->
  <section class="features-section section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Bizarre Lineage Night Vampire Abilities</h2>
      <div class="bento-grid">
        <div class="bento-card bento-large glass-card align-bottom">
          <div class="bento-watermark">
            <Moon size={120} />
          </div>
          <div class="bento-inner">
            <Moon size={40} className="bento-icon text-accent" />
            <div class="bento-badges">
              <span class="badge badge-meta">Passive Skill</span>
            </div>
            <h3>Immortality Regeneration</h3>
            <p>The core strength of the bizarre lineage night vampire is passive health regeneration. While out of direct sunlight, a bizarre lineage night vampire heals at triple the normal rate, recovering from near-fatal attacks in seconds.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bento-card glass-card">
          <Droplet size={40} className="bento-icon text-accent" />
          <h3>Blood Suck Attack</h3>
          <p>Every bizarre lineage night vampire can grab opponents to drain their life force. This move damages foes and instantly heals the bizarre lineage night vampire.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bento-card glass-card">
          <Shield size={40} className="bento-icon text-purple" />
          <h3>Superhuman Durability</h3>
          <p>A bizarre lineage night vampire receives a flat percentage reduction to all incoming physical damage, solidifying their role as a frontline brawler.</p>
        </div>
        
        <a href="/stands" class="bento-card bento-wide glass-card">
          <div class="bento-wide-content">
            <Crosshair size={40} className="bento-icon" />
            <div>
              <h3>Space Ripper Stingy Eyes</h3>
              <p>Fire highly pressurized fluid from your eyes. This is the only long-range projectile exclusive to the bizarre lineage night vampire toolkit.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="arrow-right"><ArrowRight size={24} /></div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW TO BECOME A VAMPIRE (STEP-BY-STEP) -->
  <section id="vampire-guide" class="guides-section section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">How to Unlock Bizarre Lineage Night Vampire</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Follow these specific steps to cast aside your humanity and become a bizarre lineage night vampire.</p>
      
      <div class="guide-steps">
        <div class="step-card glass-card">
          <div class="step-number">01</div>
          <h3>Find the Stone Mask</h3>
          <p>You must procure the mysterious Stone Mask item. It spawns randomly across the map or can be traded with other players. You cannot become a bizarre lineage night vampire without it.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step-card glass-card">
          <div class="step-number">02</div>
          <h3>Collect Blood Vials</h3>
          <p>Before equipping the mask, gather blood items dropped from specific NPCs. The mask requires a blood sacrifice to initiate the bizarre lineage night vampire transformation.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step-card glass-card">
          <div class="step-number">03</div>
          <h3>Wait for Nightfall</h3>
          <p>Equip the mask and use the blood items only when the in-game sun has fully set. Once successful, a dark aura will surround you, confirming you are now a bizarre lineage night vampire.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ SECTION -->
  <section class="faq-section section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Bizarre Lineage Night Vampire FAQ</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Common questions from players learning the bizarre lineage night vampire playstyle.</p>
      <FAQ items={faqs} />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BOTTOM CTA -->
  <section class="bottom-cta section">
    <div class="container" style="text-align:center;">
      <h2 class="section-title">Ready to Dominate as a Bizarre Lineage Night Vampire?</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Pair your new bizarre lineage night vampire powers with the ultimate Stand to clear servers.</p>
      <div class="hero-cta" style="justify-content:center;">
        <a href="/stands" class="btn btn-primary btn-glow">Find the Best Stand</a>
        <a href="/guides/leveling" class="btn btn-secondary glass-btn">Leveling Guide</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
/* Reusing core styles from Index but with slight variations if needed */
.hero-section {
  padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
  text-align: center;
  position: relative;
}

.hero-content {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  max-width: 800px;
}

.hero-badge {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
  border-radius: 99px;
  background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
  border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
  color: var(--color-primary);
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
  box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
}

.pulse-dot {
  width: 8px;
  height: 8px;
  background-color: var(--color-primary);
  border-radius: 50%;
  box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--color-primary);
  animation: pulse 2s infinite;
}

@keyframes pulse {
  0% { transform: scale(0.95); box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.7); }
  70% { transform: scale(1); box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0); }
  100% { transform: scale(0.95); box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(139, 92, 246, 0); }
}

.hero-title {
  font-size: 4.5rem;
  line-height: 1.1;
  font-weight: 900;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  color: #fff;
}

.gradient-text {
  display: block;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), #fbbf24);
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
  filter: drop-shadow(0 0 16px rgba(139,92,246,0.3));
  font-size: 0.65em;
  padding-bottom: 0.2em; /* prevent clipping on g/j */
}

.hero-desc {
  font-size: 1.15rem;
  color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  max-width: 650px;
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
  line-height: 1.7;
}

.hero-cta {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1rem;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.btn {
  padding: 1rem 2rem;
  border-radius: 99px;
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: all 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
}

.btn-primary {
  background: var(--color-text-primary);
  color: #000;
}

.btn-primary:hover {
  transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.05);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(255,255,255,0.2)
}

.glass-btn {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  color: var(--color-text-primary);
}

.glass-btn:hover {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
}

/* Intro Section */
.intro-content {
  max-width: 800px;
  text-align: center;
}

.intro-body {
  color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
  max-width: 750px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

/* Bento Grid */
.bento-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  grid-auto-rows: minmax(160px, auto);
  gap: 1.5rem;
}

.glass-card {
  background: var(--color-glass-bg);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-glass-border);
  border-radius: 24px;
  padding: 2rem;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  overflow: hidden;
  position: relative;
}

.glass-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  background: rgba(26, 15, 53, 0.8);
  border-color: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4), 0 0 30px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
}

.bento-large {
  grid-column: span 2;
  grid-row: span 2;
  background-image: radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1), transparent 50%);
}

.align-bottom {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: flex-end;
}

.bento-watermark {
  position: absolute;
  top: 1.5rem;
  right: 1.5rem;
  opacity: 0.15;
  pointer-events: none;
  transition: opacity 0.3s;
}

.bento-large:hover .bento-watermark {
  opacity: 0.3;
}

.bento-inner {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 90%;
}

.bento-wide {
  grid-column: span 2;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
}

.bento-wide-content {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 1.5rem;
}

.bento-icon {
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.bento-card h3 {
  font-size: 1.6rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--color-text-primary);
  margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
}

.bento-card p {
  color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  font-size: 1rem;
  margin: 0;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.bento-badges {
  display: flex;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
}

.badge {
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
  border-radius: 6px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}

.badge-meta {
  background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15);
  color: var(--color-primary);
  border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
}

.arrow-right {
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  color: var(--color-primary);
  opacity: 0.5;
  transition: all 0.3s;
}

.bento-wide:hover .arrow-right {
  opacity: 1;
  transform: translateX(4px);
}

.text-purple { color: var(--color-primary); }
.text-accent { color: var(--color-accent); }


/* Steps Section for Guide */
.guide-steps {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 1.5rem;
  margin-top: 2rem;
}

.step-card {
  position: relative;
  overflow: visible; /* to allow the number to pop out slightly if needed */
}

.step-number {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 3rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); /* very subtle */
  position: absolute;
  top: 1rem;
  right: 1.5rem;
  line-height: 1;
  pointer-events: none;
}

.step-card h3 {
  font-size: 1.4rem;
  margin-top: 1rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  color: var(--color-text-primary);
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

.step-card p {
  color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.6;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  margin: 0;
}


/* Responsive */
@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .bento-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .hero-title { font-size: 3rem; }
  .bento-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .bento-large, .bento-wide { grid-column: span 1; }
  .bento-wide-content { flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .guide-steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
</style>
